      public BasicPaymentProductsAsyncTask(android.content.Context context, PaymentContext paymentContext, C2sCommunicator communicator, List<BasicPaymentProductsAsyncTask.OnBasicPaymentProductsCallCompleteListener> listeners)
      Deprecated.
      Create a BasicPaymentProductsAsyncTask
      Parameters:
      context - Context used for reading device metadata which is sent to the GC gateway
      paymentContext - PaymentContext which contains all necessary payment data for doing a call to the GC gateway to get the BasicPaymentProducts
      communicator - C2sCommunicator which does the communication to the GC gateway
      listeners - list of BasicPaymentProductsAsyncTask.OnBasicPaymentProductsCallCompleteListener which will be called by the AsyncTask when the BasicPaymentProducts are loaded
